divs: Sighting Details Incident at Indian lake ny, I haven`t seen or spoke with my hunting buddy Tony since that year, my life has been alot of great start`s , can`t seem to get things right, now on the down side of life , I find myself going back to that night at camp sight 99 and that missing time... Just wanted to share that with someone that know`s..... thank-you Dave Harmon
